abstract: Bubba Watson leads Travelers Championship with eight-under-par 62; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Bubba Watson shot an eight-under-par 62 to take a two-stroke lead in the first round of the Travelers Championship in Cromwell, Conn.

headline.print_headline: Sports Briefing | Golf; Bubba Watson in Lead After a 62
